Catalog of 8774 stars and some information on them

Source: R/starcatalog.R
starcatalog.Rd

Here is a paragraph describing the data.

Usage

starcatalog

Format

A data frame with 8774 rows and 8 variables:

name

character. name of the star.

alt_name

character. alternate name of the star, if applicable.

vmag

double. visual magnitude

multiple

character. indicates if the star is part of a binary (W) or multiple system (A or B).

class

character. class of the star.

bv_color

double. color of the star.

parallax

double. parallax of the star.

spect_type

character. spectral type of the star.

Source

Astronomical data provided by Wesleyan's Astronomy department.
